Where ideation meets innovation.

At Benno Technologies, we're not building a technology company. We're building them all. more

As Jake and I sat advertised our intellect by using sharpies on a whiteboard, As Jake and I sat brainstorming with a dinky whiteboard and some sharpies, it was clear that we were about to do a lot of crazy things. As part of that, we were daring to make an impact in the world. Regardless of vision, we've always strived to avoid trendy industries and instead focus on providing value and being useful.

We did a lot of things that seemed crazy at the time. As part of that, we also said that you could expect us to make “smaller bets in areas that might seem very speculative or even strange when compared to our current businesses.” From the start, we’ve always strived to do more, and to do important and meaningful things with the resources we have.
